## Industries That Benefit Most From Cash-Focused CFOs

### Law Firms
Manage trust accounting, irregular settlements, and partner distributions.  
CFOs forecast unpredictable revenue and ensure compliance with client fund requirements.

### Medical Practices
Handle 60‚Äì90 day insurance delays and heavy equipment financing.  
CFOs align collections and payments to stabilize cash flow between reimbursements.

### SaaS & Cybersecurity
Balance **subscription revenue recognition** and deferred cash inflows.  
CFOs forecast runway accurately and structure pricing to improve liquidity.

### Marketing Agencies
Manage project-based cycles and contractor payouts.  
CFOs smooth cash volatility by aligning payment terms and tracking profitability by client.

