## How to Choose the Right Partner for Your Cash Goals

You‚Äôre not just hiring a service‚Äîyou‚Äôre choosing a financial co-pilot.  
Evaluate firms based on:

### 1. Relevant Industry Experience
Look for sector-specific expertise.  
Ask for **case studies** with measurable outcomes, e.g.:
> ‚ÄúReduced DSO from 52 to 34 days, freeing $180K in working capital.‚Äù

### 2. Forecasting Methodology
Ensure they use **rolling 13-week forecasts**, not static annual budgets.  
Outdated spreadsheets = outdated insights.

### 3. System Integration
Top firms use **real-time connected systems**, not manual Excel exports.  
Your dashboards should update as soon as cash hits the bank.

